Name: }bedrock.process.multithread

Parameters.Name: pTaskList
Parameters.Prompt: REQUIRED: a JSON Array which specifies processes and their parameters

Parameters.Name: pMaxThreads
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Maximum number of threads allowed to be running at one time. If zero, no limit is applied to thread count.

Parameters.Name: pRefreshRate
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Number of milliseconds to wait between checking subthread statuses

Parameters.Name: pSuccessReturnCodes
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: List of process return codes that are considered "success"

Parameters.Name: pLogOutput
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Write parameters and action summary to server message log (Boolean. Default = 0)

Parameters.Name: pStrictErrorHandling
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: On encountering any error, exit with major error status by ProcessQuit after writing to the server message log (Boolean. Default = 0)

Parameters.Name: pJson
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: JSON Object with process parameter values. This will overwrite user passed parameters for all included parameters.
